Formula for calculating Garrison:

<pre>
HP Ratio = (Current HP / Max HP)
HP Modifier = -1 * (1 - HP Ratio)^3  + 4 * (1 - HP Ratio)
Garrison DEF = Garrison Modifier * HP Modifier
</pre>

